        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Trying to test a controller action which uses the gotoRouteAndExit function of the redirector helper results in the test exiting silently; you are therefore unable to run any assertions after dispatch.\n\nNot sure if this is a bug at all, or if it is whether it's in PHPUnit or ZF.\n\nFurther, I'm not sure of the utility of gotoRouteAndExit over gotoRoute - I probably shouldn't have been using it at all, frankly!  It would be nice to have this documented."
        },
